  "text": "Functional connectivity of the ACC with the pre-SMA and the DLPFC was shown for the ''interference-related'' condition of a Stroop color-word paradigm [CITATION_1] , for a counting Stroop paradigm [CITATION_2] , respectively, supported by recent findings in a study of ACC resting-state functional connectivity [Marguilies et al., 2007] .",
